She looked to Aphrodite.  &quot;Yes, I believe my son shall be a very special Olympian.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/upersephoneqofu.showPublicProfile?language=EN>PersephoneQofU</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 22<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(6/30/01 11:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=63.topic&index=35>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> A Friend</span><hr size=1> ::smiles at Hermes and kisses him gently on the forehead:: Anytime Hermes, you sweet cousin is always here for you. ::hugs Maia back with warmth and open love:: Artemis is just jealous of Hermes I think. ::rubs rubs Maia's hands gently as they sit on the throne:: But you know, no one here is pefect, and you and Hermes will always have me as a good friend to rely on. ::Smiles to Hermes:: And I better be seeing you little one in the Underwolrd once in awhile. I need someone quick and sharp and smart to carry letters from me to the gods in the upperworld, and I think i'm looking at the right one for the job. <br>
