<br>
He was unable to remain angry, his anger would wait for another day.  The king of the gods made his way through the parting of the Olympians present to Hermes.  He gazed down at the boy god.  &quot;Hermes, my son.  You have come to fulfill your destiny.&quot;  He smiled proudly at his offspring.  Then his face took a more serious tone and his eyes danced across the faces of those Olympians present.  <br>
<br>
&quot;To those of you who have welcomed Hermes to Olympus, I am grateful; however, to those who have made his arrival and the presence of his mother a tragic event, I SHALL deal with you later.&quot;  He knew full well the words of Artemis and Ares. His eagle familiar had told all.  What fools they were to say such things not only in his temple but in full view of his familiar.<br>
<br>
He then turned his attention back to the boy.  &quot;Hermes, it is written that you shall be the great messenger of the gods as well as the ruler of travelers, merchants, rogues and thieves.&quot;  He sighed and half mumbled, &quot;Yes, apparently even thieves need a ruler over them.&quot;  He glanced at his brother Hades and then continued speaking to Hermes, &quot;It is also decreed that you shall guide dead souls to the underworld.&quot;  He watched Hermes face for any indication that this small god was distressed by his newfound duties.  &quot;You are an important and vital part of the Olympian hierarchy, my son.  Your fellow Olympians WILL strive to assist you in any way that they can as your success or failure will effect us all.&quot;  Zeus intentionally stressed &quot;will&quot; in his statement to further solidify the understanding that all Olympians would accept their new messenger god without exception.<br>
<br>
With the formalities out of the way, he walked to the throne that Maia now occupied.  His eyes danced over the throne and it's occupant, &quot;My love, I daresay that Hera has sent out a familiar in search of you.  She currently searches the mortal realm of Themiscrya and Scynthia.  If you stay to the highlands you should be safe.  I would offer you shelter here on Olympus; however, we know it is simply a matter of time before her search leads her to this place as well.&quot;  He smiled softly at his lover, &quot;I shall come to you when I am able.&quot;  <br>
<br>
He was content choosing at this moment not to dwell on the consequences of taking a consort, instead focusing on the rewards that had been reaped as a result. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showMessageRange?topicID=63.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showMessageRange?topicID=63.topic&start=41&stop=47>3</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showPrevMessage?topicID=63.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showNextMessage?topicID=63.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=63.topic&index=40><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.emailToFriend?topicID=63.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.threadControl?topicID=63.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/deleteThread.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=63.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=63.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif wi